text: Hey, so there are three types of creatures. One is bird-like, one is a fish, and one is spider-like with wings.
The spider-like ones with a lot of legs and wings are always wudsy creatures.
The fish are wudsy if they are blue and yellow. Any other colors are not wudsy.
And for the birds, if the bird is yellow/orange/green they are wudsy.
If the bird has any other color like purple, they are not wudsy.
